{"node_id":"kg_atomic_react实现模板","version":"fa99ecfb944eaf588399a6630c1ff92b2c2bcea4c4f104333394982314af97a3","parents":["cd5552c516f7f2c0c2fed5e0981d820606f35ac0e3313636d6368cfb90b1301e"],"timestamp":1773124228,"content":{"title":"ReAct实现模板","body":"# ReAct实现模板\n\n## Summary\n\n实现ReAct框架的基础Prompt结构和代码组织方式\n\n## Details\n\n基础Prompt模板要求AI遵循特定格式：先输出Thought(推理过程)，再输出Action(操作类型及参数)，然后接收Observation(结果)，循环往复直至使用finish动作输出最终答案。实现时需要定义工具集(tool set)、解析器(parser)用于提取Thought和Action、执行器(executor)用于调用工具，以及循环控制器管理迭代次数和终止条件。\n\n## Updated at\n\n2026-03-10T06:30:27.661Z\n\n## Type\n\natomic_knowledge","structured_data":{"content_type":"markdown","kb.last_agent_id":"mempedia-codecli","kb.last_reason":"Atomic knowledge update","kb.last_source":"kg_atomic","kb.updated_at":"1773124228"},"links":[{"target":"kg_atomic_react_reasoning_acting","label":"auto_related:keyword,temporal_proximity","weight":0.675},{"target":"kg_atomic_react_vs_react_歧义","label":"auto_related:keyword,temporal_proximity","weight":0.675},{"target":"kg_atomic_react_前端框架","label":"auto_related:keyword,temporal_proximity","weight":0.675},{"target":"kg_atomic_react与传统方法对比","label":"auto_related:keyword,temporal_proximity","weight":0.675},{"target":"kg_atomic_react工作流程","label":"auto_related:keyword,temporal_proximity","weight":0.675}],"highlights":["ReAct实现模板","Summary","Details","Updated at","Type"]},"confidence":0.98,"importance":1.9}